# VulkanRender v3 procedural shadow-map demo marker.
#
# The renderer recognizes this extension and builds a procedural scene with:
# - a large receiving floor
# - tall blockers for directional cascaded shadows
# - walls and steps for spot shadows
# - nearby occluders for point/sphere omni shadows
#
# It intentionally lives beside the Scene'72 example textures so the v3 preview
# can reuse the Ox Bridge IBL and ambientCG fallback texture paths.
